l-world experiments, we show that the proposed\nalgorithm outperforms competing state-of-the-art algorithms by a significant\nmargin in pose estimation accuracy, especially when deployed in complex\nlarge-scale real-world environments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 8 Sep 2019 10:28:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 25 Sep 2019 02:49:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 12 Oct 2020 04:53:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-13"}
